citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:44 am on 30-
JAN-2024.
USDA arrived at the gate and called the customer's cellphone. After no response USDA sent a text message which the
customer replied to. The customer asked to give her a moment and she would return the call. USDA waited at the facility
until the callback was received. The customer was not available for inspection.
The customer inquired about voluntarily canceling her license and instructions were provided.
End Section
